{
  "stem": "1858.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 245.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But as the war was imminent, and we realized that sooner or later, something will happen, my father, at that time-- also, there was talk about a war with Russia and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the people of my hometown were hoping that if a war comes into being, that it would be-- and Poland should lose or whatever-- it's better Germany than Russia.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "For they remembered the condition under Russia from World War I.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Of course, they had no idea, no inkling, of what Germany would become to us Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before the war, not much-- not much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were not that informed of all the details of what German-- our radios did not speak of that very much.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the newspapers did not write too much about it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And shortly before the war, oddly enough, in Poland, instead of getting ready for the war, the government officials were sending out people to check which houses need renewal, which houses need painting-- to beautify their street.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Our street was beautiful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It had flowers in the center.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And somehow-- maybe because I was still too young-- I did not feel the effect of the oncoming war until almost shortly before.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When my-- when we knew already that the war was imminent, my father and mother decided that because we were so close to the German border, that we should move inward.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was a train leaving the next morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we took with us just the necessities, locked up the house, and we all went on a train to Kielce to be with my sister.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I had two married sisters by then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "One lived in my hometown, my sister Regina.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The oldest one, she was already married and had a three-year-old little girl.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
